quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  67,15,"Ko Kanko waɗani on leydi ndin eltaandi : haray yehee e seraaji mayri, ñaamon e arsike Makko. Ko ka Makko woni ummital ngal"
  67,16,"E on hooli On wonɗo ka kammu nde O munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, Tawa yoo hindi dilla? @Corrected"
  67,17,Kaa on hooli On wonɗo ka kammu nde O wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jertinaango Am ngon
  67,18,Sellii adinooɓe ɓen ɗon ɓen fenniino. Taskii ko honno lette Am ɗen wattinirnoo
  67,19,"E ɓee yi'aali colli ɗin dow maɓɓe, hiɗi fonta gabitannji ɗi ñobba? [Wonnde] jogitaaki ɗin si wanaa Jom hinaraŋke On. Pellet, ko O reenuɗo kala huunde"
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wanaa Jom hinaraŋke On? Tigi on, heeferɓe ɓen wonaali si wanaa e nder hodo"
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si O jogitike arsike Makko on? Si ko woni, ɓe duumike e ƴaggere e woɗɗitagol"
  67,22,Kere ko on yahoowo no hippi yeeso mun ɓuri feewude? Kaa ko on yahoowo no fotondiri e laawol focciingol
  67,23,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni ko fuɗɗi on, O waɗani on nanɗe e giiɗe e ɓerɗe\". Kono fanɗii ko yettoton [neema]"
  67,24,"Maaku: \"Ko Kanko woni saakituɗo on leydi, ko ka Makko kadi woni ko mooɓitoyteɗon"
  67,25,"Hiɓe wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on goonguɓe"
  67,26,"Maaku : \"Anndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Min on ko Mi jertinoowo [tun] ɓanngina"
  67,27,"Nde ɓe yi'oyta (lette) ɗen ka ɓadii, geece yedduɓe ɓen suni geece heeferɓe, [ɓe] wi'anee : \"Ko ɗum ɗoo woni ko ɗaɓɓaynoɗon"
  67,28,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si Allah ƴettitii lam min e wonndiiɓe am maa O yurmaama men, ko hommbo daɗndata heeferɓe ɓen lette muusuɗe"
  67,29,"Maaku : \"Ko Kanko Jom hinaraŋke On. Men gomɗinii Mo, ko e Makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde anndon ko hommbo woni e majjere ɓanngunde"
  67,30,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam, si ndiyam mon ɗam wattinii ɓeeɓuɗam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilayɗam"